title: The Very Hungry Caterpillar Large Rake And Shovel
description: The Very Hungry Caterpillar Large Tools- Rake and Shovel: The rake and shovel make the perfect first gardening set for kids. The large toolscan help prepare soil, dig up treasures (and worms)and create the perfect space for new growth. Colorful and constructed with care, this set makes gardening and exploring even more enjoyable for the newest of gardeners.
